<subSubSection id="C30D69A9EB73FFC0FF24EAD0FF3BFE4F" pageId="13" pageNumber="356" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BA83A22EB73FFC0FF24EAD0FF3BFE4F" blockId="13.[151,1436,152,467]" pageId="13" pageNumber="356">
<emphasis id="B963E630EB73FFC0FF24EAD0FED1FF67" bold="true" box="[199,317,225,251]" pageId="13" pageNumber="356">Remarks:</emphasis>
having been instituted on the basis of insignificant morphological characteristics, we rank it infrasubspecific, and thus not available (
<bibRefCitation id="EF8647D3EB73FFC0FDEFEB34FD7EFE83" author="ICZN &amp; International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature" box="[524,658,261,287]" pageId="13" pageNumber="356" refId="ref17437" refString="ICZN [International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature] (2012) International code of zoological nomenclature. 4 th Edition. International Trust for Zoological Nomenclature, London. Available from: http: // www. iczn. org / (accessed 15 Feburary 2019)" type="url" year="2012">ICZN 2012</bibRefCitation>
: Art. 
<date id="FFA91CE2EB73FFC0FD2DEB34FCC2FE83" box="[718,814,260,287]" pageId="13" pageNumber="356" value="1945-10-02">10.2, 45</date>
.5, 45.6, glossary). Despite this, it was listed as a variety of 
<taxonomicName id="4C1741A1EB73FFC0FF56EB19FD8AFEDF" authority="(Gmelin, 1791)" authorityName="Gmelin" authorityYear="1791" baseAuthorityName="Gmelin" baseAuthorityYear="1791" box="[181,614,296,323]" class="Bivalvia" family="Cardiidae" genus="Parvicardium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Veneroida" pageId="13" pageNumber="356" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="exiguum">
<emphasis id="B963E630EB73FFC0FF56EB19FE58FEDE" box="[181,436,296,322]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="356">Parvicardium exiguum</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EF8647D3EB73FFC0FE21EB19FDB2FEDF" author="Gmelin, J. F." box="[450,606,296,323]" pageId="13" pageNumber="356" pagination="3021 - 4120" refId="ref17301" refString="Gmelin, J. F. (1791) Caroli a Linne, systema naturae. Tom. I. Pars VI. Beer, Lipsiae, 1100 pp. [pp. 3021 - 4120]" type="book chapter" year="1791">Gmelin, 1791</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
by Hyllelberg (2004). It would be also preoccupied by 
<taxonomicName id="4C1741A1EB73FFC0FB28EB19FED5FEFA" authority="Philippi, 1836" authorityName="Philippi" authorityYear="1836" class="Bivalvia" family="Cardiidae" genus="Cardium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Veneroida" pageId="13" pageNumber="356" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="minimum">
<emphasis id="B963E630EB73FFC0FB28EB19FA70FEDE" box="[1227,1436,296,322]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="356">Cardium minimum</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF8647D3EB73FFC0FF74EB7DFED5FEFA" author="Philippi, R. A." box="[151,313,332,358]" pageId="13" pageNumber="356" refId="ref18404" refString="Philippi, R. A. (1836) Enumeratio Molluscorum Siciliae cum viventium tum in tellure tertiaria fossilium, quae in itinere suo observavit. Sumptibus Simonis Schroppii et sociorum, Berolini, 268 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 100735" type="book" year="1836">Philippi, 1836</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. Interestingly, this 
<taxonomicName id="4C1741A1EB73FFC0FDEFEB7DFD60FEFB" box="[524,652,332,359]" pageId="13" pageNumber="356" rank="variety" variety="was">variety was</taxonomicName>
then skipped by 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8647D3EB73FFC0FCA9EB7DFC18FEFB" author="Bellini, R." box="[842,1012,332,359]" pageId="13" pageNumber="356" pagination="1 - 87" refId="ref15827" refString="Bellini, R. (1929 a) I molluschi del Golfo di Napoli (studi precedenti, l'ambiente, enumerazione e sinonimia). Annuario del Museo Zoologico della R. Universita di Napoli, 6 (2), 1 - 87." type="journal article" year="1929">Bellini (1929a)</bibRefCitation>
in the general overview of the marine molluscan species living in the Gulf of Naples. This taxon was based on a juvenile shell of 
<taxonomicName id="4C1741A1EB73FFC0FB4FEB40FACBFE16" baseAuthorityName="Gmelin" baseAuthorityYear="1791" box="[1196,1319,369,394]" class="Bivalvia" family="Cardiidae" genus="Parvicardium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Veneroida" pageId="13" pageNumber="356" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="exiguum">
<emphasis id="B963E630EB73FFC0FB4FEB40FACBFE16" box="[1196,1319,369,394]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="356">P. exiguum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, a species that was found again during samplings held in the area in 
<date id="FFA91CE2EB73FFC0FCC8EBA5FC45FE33" box="[811,937,404,431]" pageId="13" pageNumber="356" value="1975" valueMax="2018">1975–2018</date>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EF8647D3EB73FFC0FC5AEBA4FB49FE33" author="Ferro, R. &amp; Russo, G. F." box="[953,1189,405,431]" pageId="13" pageNumber="356" pagination="3 - 19" refId="ref17097" refString="Ferro, R. &amp; Russo, G. F. (1982) Le biocenosi bentoniche del Lago Fusaro. II-Malacofauna. Bollettino della Societa dei Naturalisti in Napoli, 91, 3 - 19." type="journal article" year="1982">Ferro &amp; Russo 1982</bibRefCitation>
; authors’ unpublished data).
</paragraph>
